name: Ext_R5_BiologicallyDerivedProduct_division
title: Cross-version Extension for R5.BiologicallyDerivedProduct.division for use in FHIR R4B
description: This cross-version extension represents BiologicallyDerivedProduct.division from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/BiologicallyDerivedProduct|5.0.0 for use in FHIR R4B.

element.short: A unique identifier for an aliquot of a product
element.definition: A unique identifier for an aliquot of a product.  Used to distinguish individual aliquots of a product carrying the same biologicalSource and productCode identifiers.
element.comment: `BiologicallyDerivedProduct.division` has no related element in R4B:BiologicallyDerivedProduct
